  "overview":[
    "The Fire Department continues to improve the fire protection and emergency services vital to neighborhood safety and security through capital investment in state-of-the-art technology and equipment. The five-year plan includes replacements or renovations of fire stations across the City."
  ],
  "fy_major_initiatives":[
    "The department will purchase four new Ladder trucks, four Engine trucks and one Tower Ladder truck as part of a multi-year fire apparatus replacement plan.",
    "Design for a new fire station replacing Engine 42 in Egleston Square is underway.",
    "Design for a new fire station replacing Engine 17 in Dorchester will begin.",
    "Roof and masonry construction work will begin at firehouses for Engine 4, Engine 5, Engine 14, and Engine 55.",
    "HVAC and lighting upgrades will continue at various fire stations, to improve energy efficiency and take advantage of utility rebates."
  ],
